snippet.title: World Turtles Trailer for Steam Next Fest 13 June 2022
snippet.description:
It's almost time for the Steam Next Fest (13 June 2022). If you play the new demo between 9 and 26 June, you have the opportunity of getting your name in the game upon release!

Free Demo on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1512050/World_Turtles/
Subreddit:
https://www.reddit.com/r/World_Turtles/
Discord Server:
https://discord.com/invite/2NEb4HxwhF
